keyFacts: A list of 15 phone numbers associated with Jeffrey Epstein was compiled in an email dated November 15, 2021.

The phone numbers include area codes from diverse geographic regions: 480 (Arizona), 340 (US Virgin Islands), 816 (Missouri), 347 (New York), 505 (New Mexico), 212 (New York), 407 (Florida), and 561 (Florida).
The document's subject line indicates the list was created 'for reference,' suggesting it was used for tracking, investigation, or contact purposes.
The email was sent in 2021, well after Epstein's death in 2019, indicating ongoing interest or investigation into his affairs.
The file is part of a larger data set (Set 9) and is identified as EFTA00155684, suggesting it is an official record among released documents.
